*********** BUILD ************
Type make in the current dir
Type make direct=y when you want to enable instant printing                                        
Type make CUDA=y to use monitoring with GPUs!!!!

********** RUN ***********
--> Use the script named as runController+Monitor.sh in arax_controller dir
--> In the dir of job_generatror use/modify/check run2JGns.sh

!!!!
To get power meassurments enable  POWER_TIMER in arax_controller ccmake

********** Troubleshouting *********
In case that lcudart not found
sudo ln -s /usr/local/cuda/lib64/libcudart.so /usr/lib/libcudart.so
